    <td class="roweven" valign="top" width="2000">* AnsiEsc comes in plugin + autoload format: faster vim startup, and AnsiEsc only when you want it.<br>* Now provides a :AnsiEsc command totoggle ANSI escape sequence processing.<br><br>Works with Vince Negri's conceal patch (if your vim supports VN's conceal, then the ansi-escape sequences are suppressed except on the line you're editing).</td>
</tr>
